## Anti-Patterns

| Anti-pattern | Risk | Instead |
|---|---|---|
| `as T` without a prior runtime check | Silent type unsafety — runtime explosion | Type guard or `assertNever` |
| Array index as list key | Broken reconciliation on sort/delete | Stable entity ID |
| `console.log` committed | Leaks internal data; noisy in production | Remove or use structured logger |
| `// eslint-disable` | Silences a rule that exists for a reason | Fix the root cause |
| Nested ternaries (3+) | Unreadable; AI agents get them wrong | `if/else` or `switch` |
| Prop drilling beyond 2 levels for domain data | Invisible coupling | React context scoped to the feature |
| Prop drilling beyond 2 levels for UI state | Same coupling, different layer | Zustand slice |
| `.then()` mixed with `async/await` | Inconsistent; error handling gaps | `async/await` throughout |

